            {
                "title": "Individual Income Tax",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "The individual income tax ranges from 10% to 50%. Income tax is calculated according to progressive rates. Multiple additional factors may impact overall rates such as the marital status and the number of children."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
